itemDescription: Irish aristocrat, daughter of 3rd Earl of Howth & wife of Sir Charles Compton Domville

wikipedia_page.main: Lady Margaret Frances Domville (née St Lawrence; 1840 – 9 January 1929) was an Irish aristocrat and a writer. She was also the daughter of the 3rd Earl of Howth and the wife of Sir Charles Compton Domville, 2nd Bt.
